Title: Allan Quatermain and the Temple of Skulls
Writer: David Michael Latt (screenplay), Matthew Alson Thornbury (screenplay), H. Rider Haggard (novel)
Actors: Sean Cameron Michael, Christopher Adamson, Natalie Stone, Daniel Bonjour
Plot: Allan Quatermain has been recruited to lead an expedition in search of a fabled treasure, deep within Africa. He must avoid hidden dangers.
